<paragraph id="8BDC369AFFA8FFC7FF5DFA74FD4C2745" blockId="29.[163,778,1474,1588]" pageId="29" pageNumber="614">
<emphasis id="B917EA88FFA8FFC7FF5DFA74FEBA24A9" box="[163,285,1475,1496]" italics="true" pageId="29" pageNumber="614">Comment:</emphasis>
This clade includes three subfamilies (one of them well-supported): 
<taxonomicName id="4C634D19FFA8FFC7FDCDFA56FD652486" box="[563,706,1505,1527]" class="Arachnida" family="Cosmetidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Opiliones" pageId="29" pageNumber="666" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Cynortinae">Cynortinae</taxonomicName>
